data.description: Observe the gorgeous collusion of sky burst reds & yellows just before the calm of the night on one of two decks from this West Slope home. You'll see the tips of the Narrows bridges, the Olympics and partial sound views! A modern take on this late mid-century multi-level home with its solarium next to the breakfast-coffee nook along with new metal decks wire railings, freshly painted, new carpet, updated bathrooms, new water filtration system, central heating & cooling. The lower 4th bedroom is spacious enough to be finished as a MIL ensuite for multi-generational uses. Conveniently located next to University Place, shop at Whole Foods, Trader Joes or you can walk to Titlow Beach or enjoy a burger at Lefty's only a stone's throw away.
